import React from "react"; import { Box, Typography, Drawer, List, ListItemButton, ListItemText, Divider } from "@mui/material"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; const PatientDashboard = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); // Logged-in user const user = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("user")) || { name: "Patient", role: "patient" }; // Mock data const appointments = [ { id: 1, doctor: "Dr. Alice Uwase", department: "Cardiology", datetime: "2025-11-03 09:00", status: "Scheduled" }, { id: 2, doctor: "Dr. John Niyonsenga", department: "General Medicine", datetime: "2025-11-05 11:00", status: "Scheduled" }, ]; const records = [ { id: 1, type: "Blood Test", doctor: "Dr. Alice Uwase", date: "2025-10-20", notes: "Normal" }, { id: 2, type: "X-Ray", doctor: "Dr. John Niyonsenga", date: "2025-10-15", notes: "Minor fracture" }, ]; const handleLogout = () => { localStorage.clear(); navigate("/login"); }; return ( {/* Sidebar */} {user.name} {user.role.toUpperCase()} navigate("/patient/dashboard")}> navigate("/patient/appointments")}> navigate("/patient/records")}> navigate("/patient/book-appointment")}> {/* Main Content */} Welcome, {user.name} {/* Upcoming Appointments */} Upcoming Appointments {appointments.map((appt) => ( ))}
# Doctor Department Date & Time Status
{appt.id} {appt.doctor} {appt.department} {appt.datetime} {appt.status}
{/* Recent Medical Records */} Recent Medical Records {records.map((rec) => ( ))}
# Type Doctor Date Notes
{rec.id} {rec.type} {rec.doctor} {rec.date} {rec.notes}
); }; export default PatientDashboard;
